<ServiceLayout
  title="Heartworm & Flea/Tick Prevention for Pets in Germantown, MD | Aspire Veterinary Hospital"
  description="Year-round heartworm, flea, and tick preventatives for dogs and cats in Maryland. Aspire Veterinary Hospital tailors plans for age, lifestyle, and history."
  canonical="https://aspirevethospital.com/preventative-care-germantown-md/"
